                              README                                   
                              ======                                   
                                                                       
                          HTMLtoEPUB v0.1
                           14 March 2012
                                                                       
                         Firefox extension 

                  Mozilla // University of Orleans

         web: http://sparika.github.com/Firefox-html-to-epub/          
                                                                       
=====================================================================

This project aims at allowing Firefox's users to save an HTML page as an EPUB (Electronic Book).

Install
Drag and drop the xpi file (located in /bin directory) onto your browser.

Note
You can use EPUBReader an extension to read EPUB just in your browser.

Contact
